MnO@Cnanocomposite directly grown on a conducting substrate as
electrochemical capacitors is subsequently evaluated. The MnO@C
nanocomposite grown on a Ni foam substrate is fabricated as the
working electrode, with a Pt wire serving as the counter electrode. A
